sources.title: Cab Calloway Orchestra | Hi De Ho (1947) by Josh Binney | Colorized Movie
sources.description:
Cab, an aspiring jazz musician who is trying to form is band, hires Nettie as his manager. This causes his girlfriend to become jealous and she decides to take matters into her own hands.

Original title:  Hi De Ho (1947) 

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/BRcS9-KxiMo


This film is available with subtitles in many language options.

Director: Josh Binney
Writer: Hal Seeger
Stars: Cab Calloway, Ida James, Jeni Le Gon
Genres: Colorized classics, Musical
